import { AppBar, Box, Tab, Tabs, Tooltip, Typography } from "@mui/material"
function navBar() {
  return (
    <>
      <Box>
      <AppBar>
        <Tooltip>
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{float:"left", marginTop:'5px',marginLeft:'10px'}}>LOGO</Typography>
            <Tabs sx={{float:"right"}}>
                <Tab label='Home' sx={{color:'white'}}/>
                <Tab label='About' sx={{color:'white'}}/>
                <Tab label='Contact' sx={{color:'white'}}/>
                <Tab label='login' variant="contained" sx={{float:"right",marginTop:'5px' ,color:'white'}}/>

            </Tabs>
        </Tooltip>
      </AppBar>
      </Box>
    </>
  )
}

export default navBar
